{
  "name": "feishu-doc-todo",
  "displayName": "📅 飞书文档待办自动识别",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "自动识别飞书文档中的待办表格（时间节点 + 里程碑 + 负责人），解析模糊时间，批量创建飞书日历日程并设置 deadline 提醒。",
  "author": "OpenClaw Community",
  "license": "MIT",
  "homepage": "https://clawhub.com/skills/feishu-doc-todo",
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/openclaw/skills/tree/main/feishu-doc-todo"
  },
  "keywords": [
    "feishu",
    "todo",
    "calendar",
    "deadline",
    "待办",
    "日历",
    "提醒"
  ],
  "engines": {
    "openclaw": ">=2026.3.13"
  },
  "main": "SKILL.md",
  "scripts": {
    "test": "echo \"No tests specified\""
  },
  "config": {
    "defaultReminderMinutes": 1440,
    "fuzzyTimeRules": {
      "月底": "last_day_of_month",
      "月初": "first_day_of_month",
      "月份": "15th_of_month",
      "下周": "+7_days",
      "下周初": "+7_days_first_day",
      "下月底": "next_month_last_day"
    }
  },
  "triggers": [
    "创建日历",
    "设置日程",
    "待办提醒",
    "deadline 提醒",
    "飞书文档待办",
    "文档待办转日历"
  ],
  "changelog": "## v1.0.0 (2026-03-29)\n\n- ✅ 初始版本\n- ✅ 支持读取飞书文档内容\n- ✅ 支持识别待办表格（时间节点 + 里程碑 + 负责人）\n- ✅ 支持解析模糊时间（下周/3 月底/4 月份等）\n- ✅ 支持批量创建飞书日历日程\n- ✅ 支持 deadline 提醒（提前 1 天/7 天可配置）"
}
